Subject: [EVP-ITC] ghos=
t box hacks



Colleagues,

Thank you for your concern. 
Events that unfol=
ded early this morning have prompted me to 
effectively close the Ghostboxh=
acks site for the near term. 
Do to the nature of these events it is inappr=
opriate to discuss the 
matter in a public form such as this. 

Please do n=
ot speculate on the nature of this event. I am sorry, 
after talking to cou=
ncil I removed my statement from Ghostboxhacks.
I don&#39;t want to fuel wild s=
peculation. 

I wish I could go in to greater detail, at this time I have b=
een 
advised not to.

Thank you, Everyone for your emails and concern.

-Su=
m




